02:21:58,083 --> 02:22:00,001
Lemparkan pistolmu sekarang.

2122
02:22:01,086 --> 02:22:02,128
Lempar ke tempat tidur.

2123
02:22:05,673 --> 02:22:07,092
Kuyakin dia punya pistol lain.

2124
