Joe Gage,

2222
02:27:47,849 --> 02:27:49,183
siapa kau sebenarnya?

2223
02:27:49,934 --> 02:27:50,893
Grouch Douglas.

2224
02:27:52,520 --> 02:27:54,021
Kau mengenalnya?

2225
