02:32:08,484 --> 02:32:10,277
Kami bawa jasad Jody kembali bersama kami.

2299
02:32:10,361 --> 02:32:11,612
Dia punya anak.

2300
02:32:14,699 --> 02:32:16,993
Jadi, kubunuh Warren,

2301
02:32:17,994 --> 02:32:19,745
dan kita berteman?

